---
description: Tailwind + DESIGN.md integration
globs: ["**/*.tsx"]
---

Map DESIGN.md tokens to Tailwind classes via `tailwind.config.ts` and `src/app/globals.css`.

Rules:
- Use semantic utility classes (`bg-primary`, `text-body`, `rounded-md`, `p-lg`) instead of raw hex values
- Do not use arbitrary values (e.g. `bg-[#123456]`) unless DESIGN.md defines them
- Prefer semantic tokens from the design system
- Pin Sans is proprietary — use the `font-sans` stack (Inter) defined in the config
- Reference `DESIGN.md` for component patterns; use Tailwind tokens for implementation
